des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : support@nous.technology
Amazon Alexa and NOUS Smart Home appliances work together to help you control appliances nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or change the speed setting.
There’s no need to go to the actual devices in order to adjust them - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your NOUS Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "NOUS Smart Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one NOUS Smart Home account in our "NOUS Smart Home" app;
(3). You need to have some NOUS Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our NOUS Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "NOUS Smart Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "NOUS Smart Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "NOUS Smart Home", and you'll be navigated to NOUS Smart Home login page;
(9). Input your NOUS Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on plug "
“Alexa, turn off plug "

Currently this skill supports products:
smart plug,
smart light
